cw_1201592

Class LinkedList<A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cw_1201592.LinkedList<A>

  • public class LinkedList<A>
extends java.lang.Object
    Doubly-linked lists to store annotations. There are operations to add to the start and end of the list, to calculate the length of the list, to remove the last element of the list, and to find the component at the specific index. The doubly-linked list is implemented in the inner class LLNode.
    Author:
    Boqing Liu
